name: Prana Mandrem

reviews.review_text: The location is great, the atmosphere is nice too. The food was fairly decent across what we ordered but I don’t think the cocktails were that nice but overall we had a good time and they accommodated us last minute without a booking for dinner which was very kind of the people. The service is nice and team is helpful as you make your choices.
Discovered this relaxed and upscale beachfront cafe serving up some delicious and nutritious breakfast on Mandrem beach. Staff was very polite. Highly recommend for a post-swim lovely breakfast.

One of the best beach shack and sundowners in Mandrem  providing excellent service throughout, Sipping cocktails suggested by Soreishang and Athem . Food menu is limited but serves delicious food !! The view , the music ,the crowd ……….. … your heart will beat for this place again … A must visit place in Goa !!

description:
**Discovering Prana Mandrem: A Café Oasis in Arambol**

Nestled along the serene shores of Arambol, Prana Mandrem boasts an impressive **4.3-star rating** from **775 reviews**, marking it as a beloved destination for locals and travelers alike. This charming beachfront café has become synonymous with healthy brunches, vibrant smoothies, and spectacular sunset views. With tags highlighting its offerings such as “cafe” (34 mentions), “smoothies” (22), “sunset” (22), and “bowl” (20), it’s clear that Prana Mandrem is a must-visit spot.

**Ambiance & Design**

As you approach Prana Mandrem, the inviting aura enchants the senses. The ambiance is a delightful mix of relaxed beach vibes and upscale café chic, elegantly complemented by the vibrant colors of the sunset that often graces its patrons. The design features rustic wooden furniture, comfortable seating arrangements, and earthy tones that harmonize with the natural surroundings, as showcased in customer photos [here](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdk2AM7Co57kG_KrbxOF_f_YHhbPo-EPvo6Ud6D6eOpYZxsKzFEuT3nOz1qWaj61gNz_izWj-yH6RblDZ7fUosmL1JMl9eDohGCBA53LnBefFif93vAfXNoI5Zno3M_PlyJJEpQJ9g=w375-h281-p). The open-air layout encourages a breezy, informal atmosphere complemented by the sound of waves and carefully curated music that adds to the overall relaxed vibe.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

Prana Mandrem excels at creating a delightful culinary journey that emphasizes health-conscious choices. Guests rave about the **delicious and nutritious breakfast options**, which have turned into favorites. Signature dishes like bowls adorned with fresh fruits and hearty ingredients offer both visual and gastronomic pleasure. The café's smoothie selection, noted for its refreshing flavors, often dazzles beachgoers looking for post-swim nourishment. Various dietary preferences are also accommodated, ensuring that everyone finds something enjoyable.

Patrons particularly enjoy the limited yet flavorful food menu that features delectable offerings. One reviewer noted their enjoyment of **sipping cocktails** suggested by the attentive staff, hinting at the potential for delightful mixology that enhances the café's appeal even further.

**Customer Experience & Service**

Visitors have highlighted the warm and friendly service at Prana Mandrem, making it feel like a welcoming oasis by the beach. The team is known for their helpfulness and prompt service, accommodating guests without reservations, which many found to be a pleasant surprise. The positive experiences add to the café's reputation as a friendly spot for a relaxed meal or cocktail, and anecdotes of lovely moments with friends at sunset further solidify its charm.

**Popularity & Reviews**

Prana Mandrem has captured the hearts of many, transforming into one of the **best beach shacks in Mandrem**. Customer sentiment resonates with joy and satisfaction, particularly regarding their experiences watching the sunset while enjoying refreshing drinks. Reviews on various platforms often describe it as a **must-visit place in Goa**, elevating its status among a plethora of dining options in the region.

**Utilizing Visual Content**

The stunning photos shared by customers on social media add yet another layer to Prana Mandrem’s appeal. Each image encapsulates the idyllic dining setting, gorgeous food presentations, and those enchanting sunsets that draw you in. From the colorful smoothie bowls to the lush beach surroundings reflected in the café’s décor, visual elements play a vital role in depicting the café's atmosphere [check these lovely shots here](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdn_BE7RBXAFwUPmrZX-8Tzv_aWMU_Unf9TjkuUOUhFEWGunFWdxZJ3fPcvTd9z5qtIp3fTct6MRTdb5VK9ZXm3djSet74_e8RarEsSC20_M5G9gcpAQbRnsj93sXQr51mtcgyIK=w375-h281-p).

In summary, Prana Mandrem captures the essence of coastal relaxation with its delectable menu, friendly service, and captivating views. Whether you're a local looking for a quick refresh or a traveler seeking the perfect sunset spot, this café in Arambol is sure to deliver a memorable experience.
